## 📄 **License Summary**

This project is licensed under the **MIT License**, one of the most permissive open-source licenses available.

### ✅ **What You CAN Do**

- **✨ Use** the software for any purpose, including commercial applications
- **🔧 Modify** the source code to suit your needs
- **📤 Distribute** copies of the original or modified software
- **💰 Sell** copies of the software or include it in commercial products
- **🔀 Sublicense** the software under different terms
- **🏢 Use in Private Projects** without any obligation to share changes
- **🌐 Host** the application on your own servers
- **📱 Create** derivative works and applications

### ❌ **What You CANNOT Do**

- **🚫 Hold the author liable** for any damages or issues
- **🚫 Expect warranty** or guarantee of functionality
- **🚫 Use without attribution** - you must include the copyright notice
- **🚫 Remove license** information from copies or substantial portions

### 📋 **Requirements**

When using this software, you must:

1. **📝 Include Copyright Notice**: The copyright notice and license text must be included in all copies or substantial portions of the software
2. **🏷️ Preserve Attribution**: Credit must be given to the original author (Thanattsitt Thanatt - ThannxAI)
3. **📄 Include License**: The full MIT license text must be included with distributions

