## 🏷️ **Attribution Guidelines**

### 📝 **Recommended Attribution**

When using this software, please include attribution in one of the following ways:

#### **In Source Code**
```javascript
/**
 * ThannxAI Enhanced Conversation Topic Selector
 * Copyright (c) 2024 Thanattsitt Thanatt (ThannxAI)
 * Licensed under MIT License
 * 
 * Original project: https://conversation-topics.thannx.ai
 * GitHub: https://github.com/thannxai/conversation-selector
 */
```

#### **In Documentation**
```markdown
This project uses the ThannxAI Enhanced Conversation Topic Selector
Created by Thanattsitt Thanatt (ThannxAI)
Licensed under MIT License
Source: https://github.com/thannxai/conversation-selector
```

#### **In User Interface**
```html
<!-- Footer or About section -->
<p>
    Powered by <a href="https://thannx.ai">ThannxAI</a> 
    Conversation Technology
</p>
```

#### **In Mobile Apps**
```
About > Third-Party Licenses > ThannxAI Conversation Selector
Copyright (c) 2024 Thanattsitt Thanatt (ThannxAI)
MIT License - https://opensource.org/licenses/MIT
```

